'''-{zh-hant:希拉里·詹姆斯·韦奇伍德·本恩; zh-hk:彭浩禮; zh-hans:希拉里·詹姆斯·韦奇伍德·本恩}-'''（{{lang-en|Hilary James Wedgwood Benn}}，{{bd|1953年|11月26日|catIdx=B}}），[[英國|英國]][[英國工黨|工黨]][[政治家|政治家]]，現任英国国会下院[[西約克郡|西約克郡]]中利兹（Leeds Central）選區議員，他于2003到2010年间任职于[[貝理雅內閣|布莱尔]]和[[布朗内阁|布朗内阁]]，2010年到2016年，他出任多个影子内阁要职，最近2015年5月至2016年6月曾任影子外交大臣，后被工党领袖[[杰里米·科尔宾|杰里米·科尔宾]]解雇。2016年10月，他当选为新的{{le|英国国会下院退出欧盟委员会|Exiting the European Union Select Committee}}主席。

他出生在哈默史密斯，他是工党政客[[托尼·本恩|托尼·本恩]]和教育家{{le|卡洛琳·本恩|Caroline Benn}}的儿子。他在[[萨塞克斯大学|萨塞克斯大学]]研习俄罗斯和东欧问题，并先后担任两个工会组织，{{le|科技管理人员协会|ASTMS}}和{{le|制造、科学和金融联盟|Manufacturing, Science and Finance}}的政策分析员。之后，他加入工党，又作为大伦敦下属自治市[[伊灵|伊灵区]]的市议员服务数年，成为市议会副领导人，两次作为[[北伊靈_(英國國會選區)|北伊灵]]选区工党候选人，都未成功当选。后成为传奇人物[[戴维·布兰克特|戴维·布兰克特]]的[[英国政府特别顾问|特别顾问]]，1999年赢得中利兹补选，进入国会。

本恩于2001年成为国际发展部的政务次官，于2002年调任内政部，2003年回到国际发展部，2003年10月，他被任命为国际发展大臣，主要负责伊拉克的重建工作、英国对世界各地的各种自然灾害的援助，以及寻求[[达尔富尔战争|达尔富尔战争]]解决办法等。2007年角逐工黨副领袖一位，但是被[[夏雅雯|夏雅雯]]擊敗。布朗上台后，本恩被任命为环境、粮食和乡村事务大臣，任期至2010年。他在这一职位的主要任务是打击[[牛核|牛结核病]]。

[[2010年英国大选|2010年大选]]工党失败后，本恩连续在[[哈莉特·哈曼|哈莉特·哈曼]]、[[爱德·米利班德|爱德·米利班德]]、哈曼第二任期和[[杰里米·科尔宾|杰里米·科尔宾]]四个影子内阁中担任前座长官，2015年成为影子外交大臣。2016年6月26日被科尔宾解职，引起了影子内阁成员大量辞职。

== 早年生活和教育 ==

他出生在伦敦哈默史密斯，是前工党能源大臣[[托尼·本恩|托尼·本恩]]和美国出生的教育家Caroline Benn（娘家姓 DeCamp）的第二个儿子。本恩家族四代国会议员 - 他的父亲、他的祖父空军大臣{{le|威廉·本恩，斯坦斯盖特子爵|William Wedgwood Benn, 1st Viscount Stansgate}}、他的曾祖父{{le|约翰·本恩爵士，第一代本恩男爵|Sir John Benn, 1st Baronet}}和外曾祖父{{le|丹尼尔·霍姆斯|Daniel Holmes}}，大多是[[英国自由党|自由党]]人。<ref>{{cite web|first=Harry|last=Cole|url=http://www.scribd.com/doc/207917124/Keeping-it-in-the-Family|title=Keeping it in the Family|trans_title=本恩家族世代|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223223321/http://www.scribd.com/doc/207917124/Keeping-it-in-the-Family|archivedate=2014年2月23日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

本恩先后就读于Norland地方学校、威斯敏斯特学校、荷兰公园学校和[[萨塞克斯大学|萨塞克斯大学]]，在那里他毕业于俄罗斯和[[东欧|东欧]]研究专业。本恩有一个哥哥斯蒂芬、一个妹妹梅丽莎和弟弟约书亚。<ref>{{cite book|last=Benn|first=Anthony|year=1995|title=The Benn Diaries|url=https://archive.org/details/benndiaries0000benn_h7j3|trans_title=本恩日记|page=[https://archive.org/details/benndiaries0000benn_h7j3/page/25 25]|editor-last=Winstone |editor-first=Ruth |publisher=Hutchinson|isbn=0-09-179223-1}}</ref>他回顾他的成长时说：“我在一个早餐后、晚饭和闲暇时间都谈论世界状况的家庭长大”。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/nov/09/labour.hilarybenn|title = 'I'm not a natural rebel'|trans_title = '我不是一个天生的反对派'|last = Ashley|first = Jackie|date = 9 November 2006|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2008-09-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080905151628/http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2006/nov/09/labour.hilarybenn|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 早年政治事业 ==

离开大学后，本恩成为科技管理人员协会（ASTMS）的研究员，后来成为制造、科学和金融联盟（MSF）的政策主管。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=S4x4CAAAQBAJ&pg=PT10&lpg=PT10&dq=hilary+benn+astms+head+of+policy&source=bl&ots=EMjIcPe1rV&sig=SwE-ZTvPw2yHeQhHQDKBn55QB7I&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiCqZuF1L3JAhWDKx4KHR9ZB-8Q6AEINTAE#v=onepage&q=hilary%20benn%20astms%20head%20of%20policy&f=false|title=Men Who Made Labour|trans_title=成就工党的人|work=google.co.uk|access-date=2016-12-23|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012150502/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=S4x4CAAAQBAJ&pg=PT10&lpg=PT10&dq=hilary+benn+astms+head+of+policy&source=bl&ots=EMjIcPe1rV&sig=SwE-ZTvPw2yHeQhHQDKBn55QB7I&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiCqZuF1L3JAhWDKx4KHR9ZB-8Q6AEINTAE#v=onepage&q=hilary%20benn%20astms%20head%20of%20policy&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>据说他在[[約翰·史密斯_(財政大臣)|约翰·史密斯]]任党领袖时申请了工党政策研究主任，但没有得到这份工作。<ref name=wint />

1980年，他被借调到[[英国工党|工党]]担任工党调查委员会财务小组的联席秘书。1979年，他被选为伊灵市议会议员，在那里他从1986年至1990年担任副领袖。在[[1983年英国大选|1983年]]和[[1987年英国大选|1987年]]的大选中，他是[[北伊靈_(英國國會選區)|北伊灵]]的工党候选人，皆败于保守党人哈里·格林威特。关于1983年大选失败反思，他说：“这已成为我政治经验的一部分，因为我们没有获得人家的政治信任被扫地出门，让我非常难过，就个人而言，已经在我身上留下了印记。”<ref name=whomc>{{cite news|last1=McCann|first1=Kate|title=Who is Hilary Benn? Labour's leader in waiting|trans_title=谁是希拉里·本恩，工党领袖在等待|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/labour/12030864/Who-is-Hilary-Benn-Labours-leader-in-waiting.html|accessdate=3 January 2016|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=3 December 2015|archive-date=2022-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318165848/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/labour/12030864/Who-is-Hilary-Benn-Labours-leader-in-waiting.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[1997年英国大选|1997年的大选]]中，本恩在[[庞特佛雷特|庞特佛雷特]]和[[卡斯尔福德|卡斯尔福德]]选区 Pontefract and Castleford (UK Parliament constituency)候选名单上，但最终输给了[[伊薇特·库珀|伊薇特·库珀]]，未能获得候选人资格。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/election-97-dromey-off-safe-seat-shortlist-1264876.html|title = Election '97: Dromey off safe seat shortlist|trans_title = 1997年大选：工党安全议席的候选名单|last = |first = |date = 2 April 1997|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-08-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160815045443/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/election-97-dromey-off-safe-seat-shortlist-1264876.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>在1997年大选工党政府上台之后，本恩担任当时教育和就业大臣[[戴维·布兰克特|戴维·布兰克特]]的特别顾问。<ref name="leyprof">{{cite news|last1=Ley|first1=Shaun|title=Profile: Hilary Benn steps out of late father's shadow|trans_title=简介：希拉里·本恩走出父亲的阴影|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-35005135|accessdate=25 June 2016|work=BBC News|date=6 December 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091046/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-35005135|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 工党政府任职(1999-2010) ==

1999年，在{{le|格雷特·法切特|Derek Fatchett}}世后，本恩被选为中利兹选区补选的候选人。在补选期间，他把自己描述为“只是一个本恩，不是本恩家的人”。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/366619.stm|title=The Benn dynasty|trans_title=本恩王朝|date=11 June 1999|work=BBC News|publisher=|accessdate=2 May 2010|archive-date=2007-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014000622/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/366619.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/3023827.stm|title=Profile: Hilary Benn|trans_title=简介：希拉里·本恩|date=24 June 2007|work=BBC News|publisher=BBC|accessdate=11 October 2008|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081229145823/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/3023827.stm|archivedate=2008年12月29日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>本恩赢得了1999年6月10日的补选，投票率为19％，是[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]后的补选中最小的，仅为20000多票。<ref name=nipr>{{cite news|last1=Nicholls|first1=Martin|title=Profile: Hilary Benn|trans_title=简介：希拉里·本恩|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2003/oct/06/internationalaidanddevelopment.voluntarysector|accessdate=3 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=6 October 2003|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305064134/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2003/oct/06/internationalaidanddevelopment.voluntarysector|dead-url=no}}</ref>关于投票率，他说：“我非常失望，在民主政体下出现这种情况应该引起所有人的关注。”<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/benn-jnr-joins-father-in-the-house-1099349.html|title = Benn Jnr joins father in the House|trans_title = 本恩与他父亲成为下院同事|last = Herbert|first = Ian|date = 10 June 1999|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223202134/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/benn-jnr-joins-father-in-the-house-1099349.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

他于1999年6月23日在下议院进行了第一次发言。他于2001年、2005年、2010年和2015年大选连任中利兹议员。他与[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]的工党议员理查德·科贝特（Richard Corbett）共用他的选区办公室。

=== 初任部级职务(2001-2003) ===
 
在2001年大选之后，本恩被任命为国际发展部的政务次官。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/blair-completes-his-team-ready-for-euro-push-9131337.html|title = Blair completes his team ready for euro push|trans_title = 布莱尔完成团队的组建准备引入欧元|last = Grice|first = Andrew|date = 11 June 2001|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223202127/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/blair-completes-his-team-ready-for-euro-push-9131337.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>2002年，他调任[[英国内政部|内政部]]监狱和缓刑政务次官，辅佐负责刑事司法的副大臣{{le|法尔科纳勋爵|Charlie Falconer, Baron Falconer of Thoroton}}。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/darling-takes-over-transport-hot-seat-190486.html|title = Darling takes over transport hot seat|trans_title = 阿利斯泰尔·达林接任运输大臣|last = Lyons|first = James|date = 28 May 2002|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |last2 = Merrick|first2 = Jane|archive-date = 2016-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223202053/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/darling-takes-over-transport-hot-seat-190486.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>在内政部，他领导一个调查互联网[[恋童癖|恋童癖]]的工作队，随后建议引入新的“[[儿童性诱拐|性诱拐]]”罪。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/paedophiles-to-face-jail-for-grooming-victims-on-internet-183054.html|title = Paedophiles to face jail for 'grooming' victims on internet|trans_title = 互联网恋童癖者将会因‘儿童性诱拐'罪入狱|last = Woolf|first = Marie|date = 5 July 2002|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223202216/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/paedophiles-to-face-jail-for-grooming-victims-on-internet-183054.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>2003年1月，他负责在下议院提出“[[2003年性罪行法令|2003年性罪行法令]]”。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/sex-law-reforms-leave-confusion-over-public-acts-131364.html|title = Sex law reforms leave confusion over public acts|trans_title = 性法律改革釐清公共行为的混乱|last = Burrell|first = Ian|date = 30 January 2003|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2017-10-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171012150911/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/sex-law-reforms-leave-confusion-over-public-acts-131364.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

2003年5月，他回国际发展部升任副大臣，还担任该部在下议院的发言人，因为当时的国际发展大臣{{le|瓦莱丽·艾诺斯，艾诺斯女男爵|Valerie Amos, Baroness Amos}}是[[英国上议院|上议院]]议员，无法在下院发言。<ref name="nipr" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/mini-reshuffle-fails-to-hide-division-in-government-ranks-104623.html|title = Mini-reshuffle fails to hide division in Government ranks|trans_title = 政府小改组没有改变基本人事架构|last = Grice|first = Andrew|date = 13 May 2003|work = The Independent|access-date = 6 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161223202206/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/mini-reshuffle-fails-to-hide-division-in-government-ranks-104623.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 国际发展大臣(2003-2007) ===

2003年，艾诺斯女男爵转任[[上議院領袖|上议院领袖]]，本恩由国际发展副大臣接任国际发展大臣晋升到内阁。当他把这一消息告诉家人时，他的父亲托尼说：“房子都高兴得摇晃”。<ref name=wint>{{cite news|last1=Wintour|first1=Patrick|title=Cabinet promotion for Hilary keeps it in the family|trans_title=希拉里晋升内阁保持了家族传统|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2003/oct/07/uk.internationalaidanddevelopment|accessdate=3 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=7 October 2003|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305051021/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2003/oct/07/uk.internationalaidanddevelopment|dead-url=no}}</ref>在第一次完成国际发展部在下院的问答环节后，本恩关于向外国投资者开放伊拉克的言论被自由民主党国际发展发言人汤姆·布雷克批评。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brake|first1=Tom|title=Benn's fire-sale in Iraq|trans_title=本恩的伊拉克甩卖计划|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/oct/17/iraq.iraq1|accessdate=5 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=17 October 2003|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305084404/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/oct/17/iraq.iraq1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《[[卫报|卫报]]》指出，本恩作为国际发展大臣的主要挑战之一将是“伊拉克的充分重建”。<ref name="nipr" />2004年2月，本恩说，恢复伊拉克的安全将是重建工作的“绝对根本的前提”。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/society/2004/feb/19/internationalaidanddevelopment.politicsandiraq|title = Benn details Iraq reconstruction aid|trans_title = 本恩详细解释伊拉克重建援助计划|last = |first = |date = 19 February 2004|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305005934/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2004/feb/19/internationalaidanddevelopment.politicsandiraq|dead-url = no}}</ref>

本恩监督国际发展部对[[2003年巴姆大地震|2003年巴姆大地震]]的响应，包括：“帮助协调当地与其他国际救济组织联络，并与伊朗政府合作，以确保灾区所需的设备尽快到位。”<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/dec/28/foreignpolicy.iran|title = World is pulling together for Bam|last = Benn|trans_title = 世界正在一起援助巴姆|first = Hilary|date = 28 October 2003|work = The Observer|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305102056/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/dec/28/foreignpolicy.iran|dead-url = no}}</ref>他随后监督了英国对[[2004年印度洋海啸|2004年印度洋海啸]]、[[2005年克什米尔地震|2005年克什米尔地震]]和[[2005年苏门答腊地震|2005年苏门答腊地震]]的“出色”应对。<ref name=whomc />

2004年7月，本恩公布了其设计于2003年2月的结束达尔富尔战争的五个阶段，分为阶段是：“帮助营地和其他地方的人”，“获得更多的人和更多的资源以提供这种援助”，“安全 - 紧急”，获得“苏丹政府……解除民兵武装并向人民提供保护”，最后“这场危机需要政治解决”。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/society/2004/jul/25/internationalaidanddevelopment.sudan|title = Five vital stages to achieve peace|trans_title = 实现和平的五个重要阶段|last = Benn|first = Hilary|date = 25 July 2004|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305040127/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2004/jul/25/internationalaidanddevelopment.sudan|dead-url = no}}</ref>2005年6月13日，他向[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]达尔富尔安全特派团额外提供了1900万英镑，使英国的捐款总额达到3200万英镑。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2005/jun/14/sudan.foreignpolicy|title = Minister urges Sudan to resolve Darfur crisis|trans_title = 大臣敦促苏丹解决达尔富尔危机|last = |first = |date = 14 June 2005|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305004052/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2005/jun/14/sudan.foreignpolicy|dead-url = no}}</ref>本恩在2006年达尔富尔和平谈判时领导英国谈判小组。<ref name="about">{{cite web|title=About Hilary|trans_title=关于希拉里|url=http://www.hilarybennmp.com/bio|website=Hilary Benn MP|accessdate=3 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113110708/http://www.hilarybennmp.com/bio|archive-date=2017-01-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

本恩有时也是[[联合国|联合国]]的批评者。2004年12月，他呼吁改革[[聯合國人道事務協調廳|聯合國人道事務協調廳]]（UNHCA），并说联合国难民事务高级专员（[[联合国难民署|联合国难民署]]）“应该协调，但没有足够的资源做好这项工作”。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2004/dec/30/tsunami2004.internationalaidanddevelopment|title = Benn calls for reform of UN relief efforts|trans_title = 本恩呼吁改革联合国救济工作|last = Wintour|first = Patrick|date = 30 December 2004|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305083514/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2004/dec/30/tsunami2004.internationalaidanddevelopment|dead-url = no}}</ref>他也被认为帮助建立了{{le|中央应急基金|Central Emergency Response Fund}}。<br />
本恩在[[第31届八国集团首脑会议|八国集团第31届首脑会议]]上发挥了重要作用，增加了英国的外援预算，并为最贫穷的国家争取债务减免。

2007年，新政治家杂志指出，“本恩在国际发展部的工作……常常与布什政府不一致”。特别是，本恩反对美国在非洲防治艾滋病时增加禁欲的政策，而他则采取了“减少危害”的方法。他也不理解美国的政策，说：“禁欲计划是好的，但你想禁欲，可不是每个人都这么想。”<ref name="nsinter">{{cite news|last1=Bright|first1=Martin|last2=Kampfner|first2=John|title=Interview: Hilary Benn|trans_title=希拉里·本恩的采访|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/uk-politics/2007/02/benn-interview-iraq-iran-sex|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=New Statesman|date=19 February 2007|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807034714/http://www.newstatesman.com/uk-politics/2007/02/benn-interview-iraq-iran-sex|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 2007年工党副领袖选举 ====

2006年10月下旬，本恩宣布他将参加2007年的工党副领袖选举。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/oct/27/labourleadership.labour|title = Benn may follow father in deputy leader bid|trans_title = 本恩可能像他的父亲那样竞选副领袖|last = Woodward|first = Will|date = 27 October 2006|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2006|via = |archive-date = 2014-09-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140926015217/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/oct/27/labourleadership.labour|dead-url = no}}</ref>他最早的支持者之一是[[丹尼斯·斯金纳|丹尼斯·斯金纳]]，也有人称{{le|伊恩·麦卡特尼|Ian McCartney}}在他的竞选中发挥了重要作用。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/oct/28/labour.politics|title = Benn gets Skinner's support in deputy race|trans_title = 本恩在副领袖竞选中得到斯金纳的支持|last = Branigan|first = Tania|date = 28 October 2006|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220956/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/oct/28/labour.politics|dead-url = no}}</ref>12月6日，6名工党议员签署了一份公开信，在《卫报》上发表，他们说如果本恩当选副领袖可以在党内重建“信任联盟”。<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/dec/06/labour.guardianletters|title = Benn should come to the aid of the party|trans_title = 本恩应该帮助党|last = |first = |date = 6 December 2006|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-12-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161225000234/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/dec/06/labour.guardianletters|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/dec/06/labourleadership.labour1|title = Benn 'could rebuild trust in Labour'|trans_title = 本恩可以重建对工党的信任|last = |first = |date = 6 December 2006|work = The Guardian|access-date = 5 January 2016|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305085705/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/dec/06/labourleadership.labour1|dead-url = no}}</ref>

2007年，本恩是博彩公司最青睐的工党副领袖候选人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.casinotimes.co.uk/casino-news/2007-02/william-hill-labour-170207.htm|title=Blears 8/1 For Deputy Labour Leader|trans_title=布莱尔斯进入工党副领袖选举八分之一决赛|date=17 February 2007|work=Casino Times|accessdate=11 October 2008|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630013226/http://www.casinotimes.co.uk/casino-news/2007-02/william-hill-labour-170207.htm|archivedate=2009年6月30日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>早期的民意调查也显示他是基层的最爱—在YouGov的党员调查中，本恩支持率27％，其次是教育大臣[[阿兰·约翰逊|阿兰·约翰逊]]18％，环境大臣[[戴维·米利班德|戴维·米利班德]]17％，司法副大臣[[哈莉特·哈曼|哈莉特·哈曼]]10％，[[工党主席_(英国)|工党主席]]{{le|黑索尔·布莱尔斯|Hazel Blears}}7％，威尔士大臣[[彼得·海恩|彼得·海恩]]未调查。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ukpollingreport.co.uk/blog/archives/312|title=YouGov polls on the Labour leadership|trans_title=YouGov关于工党领袖投票的调查|last=Wells|first=Anthony|date=8 September 2006|publisher=UK Polling Report|accessdate=11 October 2008|archivedate=2008年7月23日|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723160830/http://www.ukpollingreport.co.uk/blog/archives/312|deadurl=yes}}</ref>竞选于2007年5月14日在时任副领袖[[约翰·普雷斯科特|约翰·普雷斯科特]]正式辞职后开始，本恩在取得门槛所需的45个议员提名方面遇到一些困难，但是他还是获得了与其他五个候选人一样多的支持。<ref>{{cite news|date=16 May 2007|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/6658307.stm|accessdate=17 May 2007|publisher=BBC News|title=Benn short of backers|trans_title=本恩缺乏支持者|archivedate=2007年8月18日|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070818192229/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/6658307.stm|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/6663653.stm|title=Deputy hopefuls make their case|trans_title=副领袖候选人面面观|date=17 May 2007|accessdate=17 May 2007|work=BBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070826035151/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/6663653.stm|archivedate=2007年8月26日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>工党的支持提名表明，本恩获得了25％的票，后座议员[[乔恩·克鲁达斯|乔恩·克鲁达斯]]的得票率为22％，哈莉特·哈曼的得票率为19％，阿兰·约翰逊的得票率为14％，黑索尔·布莱尔斯的得票率为12％，彼得·海恩的得票率为8％。本恩在第三轮投票中被淘汰，得到了22.33％的选票。哈里特·哈曼在第五轮选举中以50.43％的选票当选。

=== 环境、食品和乡村事务大臣(2007-2010) ===

2007年，本恩被新首相[[戈登·布朗|戈登·布朗]]任命为环境、食品和乡村事务大臣，接替高升为[[英国外交大臣|外交大臣]]的[[戴维·米利班德|戴维·米利班德]]。<ref name=pro07>{{cite news|title=Profile: Hilary Benn|trans_title=简介：希拉里·本恩|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2007/jun/28/labour.gordonbrown1|accessdate=3 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=28 June 2007|archive-date=2016-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225000825/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2007/jun/28/labour.gordonbrown1|dead-url=no}}</ref>上任后，他的主要任务是应对来自牛分枝杆菌（通称牛结核病）的威胁。政府首席科学顾问{{le|戴维·柯宁|David King (chemist)}}爵士建议进行{{le|英国獾捕杀|Badger culling in the United Kingdom}}。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ghosh|first1=Pallab|title=Science chief urges badger cull|trans_title=首席科学家敦促捕杀獾|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sci/tech/7056501.stm|accessdate=9 June 2015|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2007-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071024132201/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sci/tech/7056501.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2010年4月，威尔士宣布捕杀獾，加的夫高级法院驳回了保护獾的申请。<ref name="The Guardian 16 April 2010">{{cite news |last= Morris |first= Steven |title= Badger cull in Wales gets legal go-ahead |trans_title= 威尔士的獾捕杀合法 |url= https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/apr/16/badger-cull-wales-challenge-rejected |date= 16 April 2010 |newspaper= [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location= London |accessdate= 4 December 2015 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208072712/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/apr/16/badger-cull-wales-challenge-rejected |dead-url= no }}</ref>

在{{le|2009年国会开支丑闻|United Kingdom parliamentary expenses scandal}}期间，本恩和气候变化大臣[[爱德·米利班德|爱德·米利班德]]、卫生大臣[[阿兰·约翰逊|阿兰·约翰逊]]被几家全国性报纸评为工党政府高官中廉洁的正面典型。卫报说：“当把所有威斯敏斯特议员的支出进行排名时，本恩的账单是最省纳税人钱的15个。”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2009/may/08/mps-expenses-hilary-benn-ed-miliband|title=Bargain Benn, modest Miliband (Ed, not David)|trans_title=节俭的本恩，谦逊的米利班德(爱德, 不是戴维)|first=Allegra|last=Stratton|date=8 May 2009|accessdate=12 May 2009|newspaper=The Guardian|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511084010/http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2009/may/08/mps-expenses-hilary-benn-ed-miliband|archivedate=2009年5月11日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

== 反对党 ==

2010年工党失利下野成为反对党，本恩在[[哈里特·哈曼|哈里特·哈曼]]领导的临时影子内阁中影子环境、食品和乡村事务大臣。在2010年10月8日成立的爱德·米利班德影子内阁中，本恩被任命为影子下议院领袖。2011年10月7日，米利班德改组影子内阁，本恩调任影子社区和地方政府大臣。

=== 影子外交大臣 ===

[[2015年英国大选|2015年英国大选]]后，在第二次哈里特·哈曼影子内阁，本恩被任命为影子外交大臣，接替落选的前任道格拉斯·亚历山大。6月17日，当[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]前往欧洲时，本恩代替哈里特·哈曼出席[[首相答問環節|首相答問環節]]，本恩是哈曼的非正式副手。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Chakelian|first1=Anoosh|title=Why is Hilary Benn doing PMQs?|trans_title=为什么希拉里·本恩进行首相问答|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/2015/06/why-hilary-benn-doing-pmqs|accessdate=27 November 2015|work=New Statesman|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208045001/http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/2015/06/why-hilary-benn-doing-pmqs|dead-url=no}}</ref>他问代表卡梅伦的[[乔治·奥斯本|乔治·奥斯本]]，女王陛下的“堡垒”号[[两栖登陆舰|两栖登陆舰]]是否如卫报的报道中所揭示的那样撤离地中海。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Alan|first1=Travis|last2=Rowena|first2=Mason|title=UK's Mediterranean migrant rescue ship will be withdrawn, Osborne confirms|trans_title=奥斯本证实，英国部署在地中海的移民救援船将撤离|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/jun/17/mediterranean-migrant-crisis-uk-hms-bulwark-withdrawal-george-osborne|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2016-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106180520/http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/jun/17/mediterranean-migrant-crisis-uk-hms-bulwark-withdrawal-george-osborne|dead-url=no}}</ref>新政治家杂志的George Eaton赞赏了本恩的表现，他说：“本恩的六个问题聪明地避开财政大臣擅长的经济问题而将问题投向国家安全和地中海难民危机。”<ref name=eaton>{{cite news|last1=Eaton|first1=George|author-link=George Eaton (journalist)|title=PMQs review: Osborne's unwise joke mars a solid debut|trans_title=首相问答回顾：奥斯本的首次亮相因他不高明的笑话而失色|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/2015/06/pmqs-review-osbornes-unwise-joke-mars-solid-debut|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=New Statesman|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225061510/http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/2015/06/pmqs-review-osbornes-unwise-joke-mars-solid-debut|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年9月，[[2015年工党_(英国)领袖选举|工党领袖]]和副领袖选举举行。本恩支持[[卡罗琳·弗林特|卡罗琳·弗林特]]竞选副领袖<ref>{{cite news|title=Nominations to close on Labour deputy leadership contest|trans_title=工党副领袖提名截止|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/jun/17/nominations-to-close-on-labour-deputy-leadership-contest|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2015-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151228160334/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/jun/17/nominations-to-close-on-labour-deputy-leadership-contest|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[安迪·伯纳姆|安迪·伯纳姆]]竞选领袖。<ref name=euref>{{cite news|last1=Wintour|first1=Patrick|title=Labour splits deepen over EU referendum campaign|trans_title=工党分裂使脱欧派得利|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/jun/12/labour-splits-deepen-over-eu-referendum-campaign|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=12 June 2015|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305084330/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/jun/12/labour-splits-deepen-over-eu-referendum-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref>继[[杰里米·科尔宾|杰里米·科尔宾]]在9月当选为[[工党领袖_(英国)|工党领袖]]后，本恩留任影子外交大臣，并强调工党将在所有情况下都支持继续留在欧盟。<ref name=ally>{{cite news|last1=Wintour|first1=Patrick|last2=Mason|first2=Rowena|last3=Syal|first3=Rajeev|title=Jeremy Corbyn appoints ally John McDonnell as shadow chancellor|trans_title=杰里米·科尔宾任命盟友约翰·麦克唐奈为影子财政大臣|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/13/jeremy-corbyn-shadow-cabinet-andy-burnham-labour|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=14 September 2015|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225115324/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/13/jeremy-corbyn-shadow-cabinet-andy-burnham-labour|dead-url=no}}</ref>这一点后来被本恩和科尔宾发表的一份联合声明所证实，该声明说：“工党将在全民投票中支持英国留在欧盟。”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wintour|first1=Patrick|title=Jeremy Corbyn: Labour will campaign for UK to stay in the EU|trans_title=科尔宾：工党将在全民投票中支持英国留在欧盟|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/17/jeremy-corbyn-labour-campaign-for-uk-stay-in-eu|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=17 September 2015|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009064206/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/17/jeremy-corbyn-labour-campaign-for-uk-stay-in-eu|dead-url=no}}</ref>

9月20日，本恩表示工党可以支持[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]首相在叙利亚对[[ISIS組織|ISIS]]进行空袭的计划：“我们一贯说的是，政府如果有一个建议，应该把它在下议院提出。关于空袭，我们将研究其目标。目前我们不知道提案是什么……我们将根据目标和法律基础来判断……”<ref name=back>{{cite news|last1=Mason|first1=Rowena|title=Labour could back Syria strikes despite Corbyn opposition, says Hilary Benn|trans_title=尽管科尔宾反对，工党可以支持叙利亚空袭，本恩如是说|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/20/labour-could-back-syria-strikes-despite-corbyn-opposition-says-hilary-benn|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=20 September 2015|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126135546/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/20/labour-could-back-syria-strikes-despite-corbyn-opposition-says-hilary-benn|dead-url=no}}</ref>本恩最初同意科尔宾的立场，拒绝英国在叙利亚发动针对黎凡特伊斯兰国的空袭和任何干预的建议。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/hilary-benn-shadow-foreign-secretary-says-labour-wont-back-air-strikes-on-syria-a6734651.html|title = Hilary Benn: Shadow Foreign Secretary says Labour won't back air strikes on Syria|trans_title = 希拉里·本恩: 影子外交大臣说工党不会支持空袭叙利亚|publisher = |date = 15 November 2015|accessdate = 4 December 2015|newspaper = The Independent on Sunday|last = McTague|first = Tom|archive-date = 2020-04-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200426183117/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/hilary-benn-shadow-foreign-secretary-says-labour-wont-back-air-strikes-on-syria-a6734651.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>但在[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|2015年11月巴黎袭击事件]]发生不久之后，本恩支持卡梅伦首相制定的计划，并说他不会因与科尔宾意见不同而辞职，因为自己“做了影子外交大臣该做的工作”。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Casalicchio|first1=Emilio|title=Hilary Benn: I won't quit|trans_title=本恩：我不会辞职|url=https://www.politicshome.com/party-politics/articles/story/hilary-benn-i-wont-quit|accessdate=27 November 2015|work=Politics Home|date=27 November 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208143204/https://www.politicshome.com/party-politics/articles/story/hilary-benn-i-wont-quit|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Mason|first1=Rowena|last2=Boffe|first2=Daniel|title=Hilary Benn tells Corbyn: I'm doing my job in supporting Syria airstrikes|trans_title=本恩告诉科尔宾：我支持空袭叙利亚是尽我本职|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/nov/27/hilary-benn-wont-resign-over-support-syria-airstrikes?CMP=twt_gu|accessdate=27 November 2015|work=The Guardian|date=27 November 2015|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208070250/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/nov/27/hilary-benn-wont-resign-over-support-syria-airstrikes?CMP=twt_gu|dead-url=no}}</ref>他曾投票赞成2003年的[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]和[[2011年多国武装干涉利比亚|2011年多国武装干涉利比亚]]，<ref name="TWFY H Benn">{{cite web |title= Hilary Benn » Voting Record |url= https://www.theyworkforyou.com/mp/10669/hilary_benn/leeds_central/votes |website= theyworkforyou.com |accessdate= 2 December 2015 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208215117/http://www.theyworkforyou.com/mp/10669/hilary_benn/leeds_central/votes |dead-url= no }}</ref>但投票反对2013年对叙利亚总统[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]的军事干预。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/syria-how-your-mp-vote-2238483|title=Syria: How did your MP vote in the Commons over military action?|trans_title=军事干涉叙利亚：你的议员是怎样投的票？|work=Daily Mirror|first=Jason|last=Beattie|date=30 August 2013|access-date=2016-12-24|archive-date=2022-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313112410/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/syria-how-your-mp-vote-2238483|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Barack_Obama_and_Opposition_leader_Jeremy_Corbyn.jpg|325px]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]。]]
2015年12月2日，本恩在关于空袭叙利亚黎凡特伊斯兰国的下议院辩论中作反对党正式总结陈词。发言反对科尔宾的立场，赞成政府的动议。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-34980504|title=Syria vote: Cameron and Corbyn clash over air strikes|trans_title=叙利亚投票;卡梅伦和科尔宾因空袭而冲突|publisher=BBC News|date=2 December 2015|accessdate=3 December 2015|archive-date=2021-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216105005/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-34980504|dead-url=no}}</ref>演讲得到了下院议事厅两侧议员的赞扬，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-34990957|title=Hilary Benn's Syria speech applauded by MPs|trans_title=希拉里·本恩的叙利亚讲话被国会议员赞扬|accessdate=2016-12-24|archive-date=2015-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206021447/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-34990957|dead-url=no}}</ref>议员们用通常不允许的掌声向本恩致意。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Wheeler|first1=Brian|title=Why are MPs banned from clapping?|trans_title=为什么国会议员被禁止鼓掌？|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-32913113|website=BBC|accessdate=3 December 2015|archive-date=2022-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215003711/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-32913113|dead-url=no}}</ref>少数影子内阁成员也投票赞成空袭叙利亚，该议案以高于预期的174票多数获得通过。<ref>{{cite news|last=Dathan|first=Matt|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/syria-air-strikes-majority-of-shadow-cabinet-backed-jeremy-corbyn-but-more-than-a-third-of-labour-a6758166.html|title=Syria air strikes: Majority of Shadow Cabinet supported Jeremy Corbyn but third of Labour MPs rebelled|trans_title=叙利亚空袭:多数影子内阁成员支持科尔宾但有三分之一的工党议员反对|work=The Independent|date=3 December 2015|accessdate=3 December 2015|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426180703/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/syria-air-strikes-majority-of-shadow-cabinet-backed-jeremy-corbyn-but-more-than-a-third-of-labour-a6758166.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>本恩的演讲被描述为“下议院历史上真正伟大的演讲之一”。<ref>{{cite web |last=Riley-Smith |first=Ben |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/12032191/hilary-benn-labour-party-leader-jeremy-corbyn.html |title=Hilary Benn will never lead the Labour Party, say Jeremy Corbyn's allies |trans_title=希拉里·本恩将永远不会领导工党，杰里米·科尔宾的盟友说 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |date= |accessdate=3 December 2015 |archive-date=2019-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705221424/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/12032191/hilary-benn-labour-party-leader-jeremy-corbyn.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在第二天向英国广播公司（BBC）发表讲话时，影子财政大臣[[约翰·麦克唐奈|约翰·麦克唐奈]]（John McDonnell）将本恩的演讲与[[托尼·布莱尔|托尼·布莱尔]]首相在2003年伊拉克战争之前的讲话进行了比较。麦克唐纳把它描述为“优秀”的教科书式的演讲，但补充说：“巧舌如簧不见得是什么好事，它可能会让人犯一些追悔莫及的大错。”<ref name="BBC News 3 December 2015">{{cite web | title= Hilary Benn speech reminded me of Blair – McDonnell | trans_title= 本恩得演讲让我想起了布莱尔—麦克唐奈 | url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-34993438 | author= <!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> | date= 3 December 2015 | website= [[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] | accessdate= 3 December 2015 | archive-date= 2020-11-08 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111825/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-34993438 | dead-url= no }}</ref>根据工党议员[[杰米·里德|杰米·里德]]观察，本恩演讲后，在科尔宾眼里，本恩成为“往好处说是忤逆，往坏处说就是叛徒。”<ref name=reed>{{cite news|last1=Reed|first1=Jamie|authorlink1=Jamie Reed|title=If Jeremy Corbyn moves Hilary Benn, he'll hurt himself|trans_title=如果科尔宾调动本恩，他将害了他自己|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/staggers/2016/01/if-jeremy-corbyn-moves-hilary-benn-hell-hurt-himself|accessdate=2016-01-04|work=New Statesman|date=2016-01-04|archive-date=2016-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106012338/http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/staggers/2016/01/if-jeremy-corbyn-moves-hilary-benn-hell-hurt-himself|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年1月，本恩在联合国报告泄漏沙特违反国际人道主义法对平民目标进行了“广泛和系统的”攻击后，批评英国参与[[沙特领导的干预也门行动|沙特领导的干预也门行动]]。<ref>"[https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jan/27/labour-raises-pressure-on-cameron-to-explain-yemen-involvement Labour seeks details of UK role in Saudi-led airstrikes on Yemen] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jan/27/labour-raises-pressure-on-cameron-to-explain-yemen-involvement |date=20161016180953 }}". ''The Guardian.'' 27 January 2016.</ref>

2016年6月25日，[[观察家报|观察家报]]透露，本恩“整个周末他打电话暗示他的同事议员们如果党内有明显的反对科尔宾的势头，他会向科尔宾挑明让他退出。他还要求影子内阁同事与他一起辞职，如果工党领袖忽略了这个请求的话。”<ref name="seeks">{{cite news|last1=Boffey|first1=Daniel|title=Hilary Benn seeks shadow cabinet backing to oust Corbyn|trans_title=本恩寻求影子内阁支持驱逐科尔宾|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/25/hilary-benn-jeremy-corbyn-labour-leadership-eu-referendum-brexit|accessdate=26 June 2016|work=The Observer|date=25 June 2016|archive-date=2016-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625223728/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/25/hilary-benn-jeremy-corbyn-labour-leadership-eu-referendum-brexit|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月26日凌晨本恩致电科尔宾说，在后者的领导下，工党议员和影子内阁成员“对我们赢得大选没有信心”。然后科尔宾开除了本恩的影子外交大臣一职。当日凌晨03:30本恩发表声明：“现在已经清楚地看到，工党议员和影子内阁都关注杰里米·科尔宾对我们党的领导。特别是，如果杰里米继续领导，我们对赢得下一届大选的能力没有信心，尤其是下次大选可能比预期更早。”<ref name="half">{{cite news|last1=Asthana|first1=Anushka|last2=Boffey|first2=Daniel|last3=Phipps|first3=Claire|title=Half of Labour shadow cabinet set to resign after Hilary Benn sacked|trans_title=希拉里·本恩被开除后，一半影子内阁成员辞职|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/26/hilary-benn-revolt-jeremy-corbyn|accessdate=26 June 2016|work=The Observer|date=26 June 2016|archive-date=2016-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626010403/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/26/hilary-benn-revolt-jeremy-corbyn|dead-url=no}}</ref>上午晚些时候，影子卫生大臣{{le|海蒂·亚历山大|Heidi Alexander}}也辞职了。一天内，又有影子内阁的八名成员相继辞职。<ref name="syres">{{cite news|last1=Syal|first1=Rajeev|last2=Perraudin|first2=Frances|title=Shadow cabinet resignations: who has gone and who is staying|trans_title=影子内阁大辞职：谁去谁留？|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/26/labour-shadow-cabinet-resignations-jeremy-corbyn-who-has-gone|accessdate=26 June 2016|work=The Guardian|date=26 June 2016|archive-date=2016-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722213447/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/26/labour-shadow-cabinet-resignations-jeremy-corbyn-who-has-gone|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 脱欧事务委员会主席 ===

2016年9月，本恩宣布他打算成为一个新的下议院专责委员会退出欧盟委员会的主席。他说，他的目的是“为英国人民得到最好的交易”。他的出马得到前工党领袖爱德·米利班德以及其他工党高层支持，包括[[安吉拉·伊格尔|安吉拉·伊格尔]]、[[丹·贾维斯|丹·贾维斯]]和[[安迪·伯纳姆|安迪·伯纳姆]]。他的竞选对手是{{le|凯蒂·霍伊|Kate Hoey}}，一个工党同事和一个脱欧派支持者。结果于10月19日宣布，本恩得到330票，霍伊得209票，所以本恩成为新的主席。<ref>{{cite news|last=Elgot|first=Jessica|title=Hilary Benn and Kate Hoey compete for key Brexit scrutiny role|trans_title=本恩和霍伊竞争脱欧过程的关键角色|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/18/hilary-benn-kate-hoey-compete-brexit-scrutiny-committee|accessdate=19 October 2016|work=The Guardian|date=18 October 2015|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020045113/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/18/hilary-benn-kate-hoey-compete-brexit-scrutiny-committee|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pro-Remain MP Hilary Benn heads Brexit Commons Committee|trans_title=留欧派议员希拉里·本恩领导脱欧委员会|url=http://news.sky.com/story/pro-remain-mp-hilary-benn-heads-brexit-commons-committee-10623788|accessdate=19 October 2016|work=Sky News|date=19 October 2015|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020040355/http://news.sky.com/story/pro-remain-mp-hilary-benn-heads-brexit-commons-committee-10623788|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Syal|first=Rajeev|title=MPs elect Hilary Benn to chair Brexit select committee|trans_title=本恩议员当选脱欧专责委员会主席|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/19/mps-elect-hilary-benn-to-chair-brexit-select-committee|accessdate=19 October 2016|work=The Guardian|date=19 October 2015|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020045740/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/19/mps-elect-hilary-benn-to-chair-brexit-select-committee|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 政治观点 ==

本恩支持英国维持核威慑。<ref name=split>{{cite news|last1=Watt|first1=Nicholas|last2=Wintour|first2=Patrick|last3=Mason|first3=Rowena|title=Labour split on defence grows as Maria Eagle criticises Corbyn over Trident|8=|trans_title=工党因国防预算增长而分裂，影子国防大臣玛利亚·伊格尔在三叉戟导弹问题上批评科尔宾|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/30/labour-split-on-defence-grows-as-eagle-criticises-corbyn-over-trident|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=The Guardian|date=30 September 2015|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129075131/http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/30/labour-split-on-defence-grows-as-eagle-criticises-corbyn-over-trident|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 私人生活 ==

1973年，在大学期间，本恩和同学Rosalind Caroline Retey结婚。她在1979年死于癌症，年26岁。<ref>{{cite book|last=Benn|first=Anthony|year=1995 |title=The Benn Diaries|url=https://archive.org/details/benndiaries0000benn_h7j3|trans_title=本恩生平|page=[https://archive.org/details/benndiaries0000benn_h7j3/page/476 476]|editor-last=Winstone |editor-first=Ruth|publisher=[[Hutchinson_(publisher)|Hutchinson]]|isbn=0-09-179223-1}}</ref>他随后于1982年与萨莉·克里斯蒂娜·克拉克结婚。<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.ukwhoswho.com/view/article/oupww/whoswho/U7219/ |title=Who's Who |trans_title=谁是谁 |publisher=A & C Black |year=2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Benn|first=Anthony|year= 1995|title=The Benn Diaries|url=https://archive.org/details/benndiaries0000benn_h7j3|trans_title=本恩生平|page=[https://archive.org/details/benndiaries0000benn_h7j3/page/538 538]|editor-last=Winstone |editor-first=Ruth |publisher=Hutchinson|isbn=0-09-179223-1}}</ref>他有四个孩子。<ref>{{cite web |last=McCann |first=Kate |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/labour/12030864/Who-is-Hilary-Benn-Labours-leader-in-waiting.html |title=Who is Hilary Benn? Labour's leader in waiting |trans_title=谁是希拉里·本恩？工党领袖在等待 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=3 December 2015 |accessdate=3 December 2015 |archive-date=2022-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318165848/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/labour/12030864/Who-is-Hilary-Benn-Labours-leader-in-waiting.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

像他父亲一样，是禁酒主义者和素食主义者。<ref name="Ashley_J_11Oct08">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2006/nov/09/labour.hilarybenn|title='I'm not a natural rebel'|trans_title='我不是天生的反叛者|last=Ashley|first=Jackie|date=9 November 2006|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[Guardian_News_&_Media|Guardian News & Media]]|accessdate=11 October 2008|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905151628/http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2006/nov/09/labour.hilarybenn|archivedate=2008年9月5日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

== 获奖 ==

2015年，他因在国际发展部的工作而被提议入围{{le|民间外交家|Grassroot Diplomat}}奖，并保留在《民间外交家点将录》的目录中。<ref>{{cite news|title=Grassroot Diplomat Who's Who |url=http://www.grassrootdiplomat.org/whoswho/ |accessdate=27 April 2015 |work=Grassroot Diplomat |date=15 March 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520125406/http://www.grassrootdiplomat.org/whoswho/ |archivedate=20 May 2015 }}</ref>

